            <description><![CDATA[We're excited to launch the official documentation site for the Isolated Local LLM Deployment & Monitoring Stack!]]></description>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>We're excited to launch the official documentation site for the <strong>Isolated Local LLM Deployment &amp; Monitoring Stack</strong>!</p>
<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="-whats-new">🚀 What's New<a href="https://mohamedaminehamdi.github.io/Isolated-Local-LLM-Deployment-Monitoring-Stack/blog/welcome-llm-docs#-whats-new" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to 🚀 What's New" title="Direct link to 🚀 What's New">​</a></h2>
<p>This comprehensive documentation site provides:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Step-by-step guides</strong> for deploying your local LLM environment</li>
<li><strong>Detailed monitoring setup</strong> with Prometheus and Grafana</li>
<li><strong>Security best practices</strong> for air-gapped deployments</li>
<li><strong>Troubleshooting guides</strong> for common issues</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="-documentation-structure">📚 Documentation Structure<a href="https://mohamedaminehamdi.github.io/Isolated-Local-LLM-Deployment-Monitoring-Stack/blog/welcome-llm-docs#-documentation-structure" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to 📚 Documentation Structure" title="Direct link to 📚 Documentation Structure">​</a></h2>
<p>Our documentation is organized into clear sections:</p>
<h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="-getting-started">🎯 <a href="https://mohamedaminehamdi.github.io/Isolated-Local-LLM-Deployment-Monitoring-Stack/docs/intro">Getting Started</a><a href="https://mohamedaminehamdi.github.io/Isolated-Local-LLM-Deployment-Monitoring-Stack/blog/welcome-llm-docs#-getting-started" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to -getting-started" title="Direct link to -getting-started">​</a></h3>
<p>Jump right in with our quick start guide. Get your LLM environment running in under 5 minutes!</p>
<h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="-llm-deployment">🔧 <a href="https://mohamedaminehamdi.github.io/Isolated-Local-LLM-Deployment-Monitoring-Stack/docs/llm-deployment">LLM Deployment</a><a href="https://mohamedaminehamdi.github.io/Isolated-Local-LLM-Deployment-Monitoring-Stack/blog/welcome-llm-docs#-llm-deployment" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to -llm-deployment" title="Direct link to -llm-deployment">​</a></h3>
<p>Deep dive into Ollama configuration, model management, and Open WebUI setup.</p>
<h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="-monitoring-stack">📊 <a href="https://mohamedaminehamdi.github.io/Isolated-Local-LLM-Deployment-Monitoring-Stack/docs/monitoring">Monitoring Stack</a><a href="https://mohamedaminehamdi.github.io/Isolated-Local-LLM-Deployment-Monitoring-Stack/blog/welcome-llm-docs#-monitoring-stack" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to -monitoring-stack" title="Direct link to -monitoring-stack">​</a></h3>
<p>Learn how to set up comprehensive monitoring with Prometheus, Grafana, cAdvisor, and Node Exporter.</p>
<h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="-security--isolation">🔒 <a href="https://mohamedaminehamdi.github.io/Isolated-Local-LLM-Deployment-Monitoring-Stack/docs/security">Security &amp; Isolation</a><a href="https://mohamedaminehamdi.github.io/Isolated-Local-LLM-Deployment-Monitoring-Stack/blog/welcome-llm-docs#-security--isolation" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to -security--isolation" title="Direct link to -security--isolation">​</a></h3>
<p>Understand the security features and network isolation that make this stack enterprise-ready.</p>
<h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="️-troubleshooting">🛠️ <a href="https://mohamedaminehamdi.github.io/Isolated-Local-LLM-Deployment-Monitoring-Stack/docs/troubleshooting">Troubleshooting</a><a href="https://mohamedaminehamdi.github.io/Isolated-Local-LLM-Deployment-Monitoring-Stack/blog/welcome-llm-docs#%EF%B8%8F-troubleshooting" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to ️-troubleshooting" title="Direct link to ️-troubleshooting">​</a></h3>
<p>Find solutions to common issues and learn debugging techniques.</p>
<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="-key-features-covered">🌟 Key Features Covered<a href="https://mohamedaminehamdi.github.io/Isolated-Local-LLM-Deployment-Monitoring-Stack/blog/welcome-llm-docs#-key-features-covered" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to 🌟 Key Features Covered" title="Direct link to 🌟 Key Features Covered">​</a></h2>
<ul>
<li><strong>One-command deployment</strong> with Docker</li>
<li><strong>Air-gapped compatibility</strong> for secure environments</li>
<li><strong>Real-time monitoring</strong> and alerting</li>
<li><strong>Model management</strong> and optimization</li>
<li><strong>Performance tuning</strong> and resource management</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="-contributing">🤝 Contributing<a href="https://mohamedaminehamdi.github.io/Isolated-Local-LLM-Deployment-Monitoring-Stack/blog/welcome-llm-docs#-contributing" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to 🤝 Contributing" title="Direct link to 🤝 Contributing">​</a></h2>
<p>Found an issue with the documentation? Have suggestions for improvement?</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://github.com/mohamedaminehamdi/Isolated-Local-LLM-Deployment-Monitoring-Stack/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Report issues</a></li>
<li><a href="https://github.com/mohamedaminehamdi/Isolated-Local-LLM-Deployment-Monitoring-Stack/discussions" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Join discussions</a></li>
<li><a href="https://github.com/mohamedaminehamdi/Isolated-Local-LLM-Deployment-Monitoring-Stack/tree/main/docs" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Contribute to docs</a></li>
</ul>
<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="-whats-next">🎯 What's Next?<a href="https://mohamedaminehamdi.github.io/Isolated-Local-LLM-Deployment-Monitoring-Stack/blog/welcome-llm-docs#-whats-next" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to 🎯 What's Next?" title="Direct link to 🎯 What's Next?">​</a></h2>
<p>We're continuously improving the documentation based on community feedback. Upcoming additions include:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Advanced configuration guides</strong></li>
<li><strong>Performance optimization tutorials</strong></li>
<li><strong>Custom model integration</strong></li>
<li><strong>Scaling strategies</strong></li>
</ul>
<p>Ready to get started? Head over to our <a href="https://mohamedaminehamdi.github.io/Isolated-Local-LLM-Deployment-Monitoring-Stack/docs/intro">Getting Started Guide</a> and deploy your first LLM in minutes!</p>
<hr>
<p>Happy deploying! 🚀</p>]]></content:encoded>
